Alumni Achievements

Dance alumna Yeo Chan Yee in the lead role in “Paquita” and "Concerto"

Published on Jan 28, 2016

Dance alumna Yeo Chan Yee in the lead role in “Paquita” and "Concerto"

Photo credit: Amber Griffin

Congratulations to our Dance alumna Yeo Chan Yee who performed as the lead role in the Classical repertoire of “Paquita” and Kenneth MacMillan's "Concerto" at the graduation showcase of the New Zealand School of Dance (NZSD)! Chan Yee will be commencing her apprenticeship with the Singapore Dance Theatre in 2016.
